Passing a Two-Dimensional Array to and from a Method
A two-dimensional array can be passed to a method just as a one-dimensional array
can be passed to a method. The following program implements a method that
calculates and outputs the average of the exam scores for each student in the
class. The studentsAvg method is called from the main method:
